No. 09-868. Ashbel T. Wall, II, Director, Rhode Island Department of Corrections, Petitioner v. Khalil Kholi. 561 U.S. 1023, 130 S. Ct. 3536,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1088,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5346. June 28, 2010.

Motion of respondent for appointment of counsel granted. Judith H. Mizner, Esq., of Boston, Massachusetts, is appointed to serve as counsel for the respondent in this case.
